int main()
{int n,xll[3],yll[3],xur[3],yur[3],i;

 {for(i=0;i<2;i++)
  scanf("%d%d%d%d",&xll[i],&yll[i],&xur[i],&yur[i]);

  else if(yur[1]<=yll[0]) printf("No Overlap\n");        
          
  else if(yur[1]<=yll[0]) printf("No Overlap\n");
  
  else
   {xll[2]=(xll[0]>xll[1])?xll[0]:xll[1];        
    yll[2]=(yll[0]>yll[1])?yll[0]:yll[1];

    printf("%d %d %d %d\n",xll[2],yll[2],xur[2],yur[2]);
   }

}
